SIMPLE: cranky
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cranky
<hw>Crank"y</hw> <pr>(-?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Full of
spirit; crank.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Addicted to crotchets and whims; unreasonable in
opinions; crotchety.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Unsteady; easy to upset; crank.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Crannied</ent>⟦br⟧
